                </li>
                <li class="text-black flex text-base pb-6 items-center">
                  <span class="mr-2.5 flex h-[40px] w-full max-w-[40px] items-center justify-center rounded-full ring-[1.5px] ring-inset ring-blue-500 text-base text-white">
                    <%=image_tag "fastci/icon-clean-code.svg", alt: ""%>
                  </span>
                  It ensures cleaner code and a healthier application by tracking individual commit trends and performance.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
